{"title":"crapy-speedup","slug":"crapy-speedup","date":"2019-01-30T11:46:13.000Z","updated":"2019-02-03T15:46:43.342Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/crapy-speedup.json","photos":[],"link":"","excerpt":"(二) 让爬虫飞起来(crapy-speedup)多线程 multithreading$\\to$threading库多进程 multiprocess协程 gevent异步 asyio [Figure] ","covers":["https://i.loli.net/2019/01/30/5c518f78e69c3.gif"],"content":"<h1 id=\"二-让爬虫飞起来-crapy-speedup\"><a href=\"#二-让爬虫飞起来-crapy-speedup\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"(二) 让爬虫飞起来(crapy-speedup)\"></a>(二) 让爬虫飞起来(<code>crapy-speedup</code>)</h1><ul>\n<li>多线程 <code>multithreading</code>$\\to$<code>threading</code>库</li>\n<li>多进程 <code>multiprocess</code></li>\n<li>协程 <code>gevent</code></li>\n<li>异步 <code>asyio</code></li>\n</ul>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.loli.net/2019/01/30/5c518f78e69c3.gif\" alt=\"tumblr_mvl7699VoR1rqg00io8_r1_250.gif\"><br><a id=\"more\"></a></p>\n<p><code>关键词:</code> <code>同步</code> <code>锁</code> </p>\n<h2 id=\"1-多线程-multithreading\"><a href=\"#1-多线程-multithreading\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"1. 多线程 multithreading\"></a>1. 多线程 <code>multithreading</code></h2><p>Python中的线程会在一个单独的系统级线程中执行（比如说一个 POSIX 线程或者一个 Windows 线程），这些线程将由操作系统来全权管理。</p>\n","categories":[],"tags":[{"name":"python","slug":"python","count":4,"path":"api/tags/python.json"}]}